<!-- ════════════════════ FOUNDATIONS ════════════════════ -->
<section class="sec" id="foundations">
  <div class="sec-h"><span class="ix">00</span><h2>Foundations</h2></div>
  <p class="sec-sub">The token system. Lilac is the primary accent (interactive, model/AI, telemetry); amber is the value / money / premium accent; steel, jade and coral carry secondary, positive and negative meaning. Everything sits on a near-black blue void with hairline dividers and a glassy panel surface.</p>

  <div class="sub-l">Accent palette</div>
  <div class="swatches">
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#A7A9EC"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Lilac · primary</div><div class="hx">#A7A9EC · --lilac</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#C7C8F6"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Lilac hi</div><div class="hx">#C7C8F6 · --lilac-hi</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#6F72C9"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Lilac deep</div><div class="hx">#6F72C9 · --lilac-deep</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#E2B266"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Amber · value</div><div class="hx">#E2B266 · --amber</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#82B2D0"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Steel · data</div><div class="hx">#82B2D0 · --steel</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#6FC79A"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Jade · positive</div><div class="hx">#6FC79A · --jade</div></div></div>
    <div class="sw"><div class="chipc" style="background:#E08A8A"></div><div class="meta"><div class="nm">Coral · negative</div><div class="hx">#E08A8A · --coral</div></div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid cols-2 mt16">
    <div class="cell">
      <div class="cell-t">Surface scale · void → hull</div>
      <div class="scale-row">
        <div class="s" style="background:#08090F"><span>void</span></div>
        <div class="s" style="background:#0B0D16"><span>void-2</span></div>
        <div class="s" style="background:#12131D"><span>hull</span></div>
        <div class="s" style="background:#161826"><span>hull-2</span></div>
        <div class="s" style="background:#1B1D2B"><span>hull-3</span></div>
      </div>
      <span class="cap"><b>Panels</b> render as a glass layer over the void: <code>rgba(20,22,34,.62)</code> + <code>backdrop-blur(16px)</code>.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cell">
      <div class="cell-t">Ink scale · primary → faint</div>
      <div class="scale-row">
        <div class="s" style="background:#E7E9F3"><span style="color:#222">ink</span></div>
