        <div class="s" style="background:#6E7290"><span>ink-3</span></div>
        <div class="s" style="background:#494D66"><span>ink-4</span></div>
      </div>
      <span class="cap">Hairlines are translucent: <code>rgba(150,156,190,.13&ndash;.40)</code>. Never solid grey rules.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid cols-3 mt16">
